day1.dayDesc: Plenty of clouds with a couple of showers, mainly early; breezy

day2.dayDesc: A couple of showers in the morning; otherwise, rather cloudy

day3.dayDesc: A shower in spots in the morning; otherwise, intervals of clouds and sunshine
day3.nightDesc: Clear to partly cloudy in the evening, then becoming cloudy

day4.dayDesc: A morning shower in spots; otherwise, considerable cloudiness

day5.dayDesc: Cloudy with a shower in spots in the morning, then turning breezy
day5.nightDesc: Cloudy with occasional rain and a thunderstorm late
